Sentence: Roman numerals represent different microscopic slides and Arabic numerals different cell lines labelled as follows: ( I) wt cells ( 1) labelled with 2 - mu m beads, XpdTTD / TTD cells ( 2) with 0. 79 - mu m beads, and XpdTTD / KO cells ( 3) with no beads; ( II) wt cells ( 1) labelled with 0. 79 - mu m beads and XpdTTD / + XPCS cells ( 4) with no beads; and ( III) wt cells ( 1) labelled with 0. 79 - mu m beads and XpdTTD / + XP cells ( 5) with no beads.
